StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetMudStaging_ZipsToArchive]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
AS
SELECT MF.ZIP AS Zipcode, MR.REGION_ID AS RegionID, MR.DIST_ID AS DistrictID, MR.REGION_NAME AS Organiza.onName, NULL AS OldRecord, NULL AS NewRecord FROM [dbo].[MUD_FILE] MF INNER JOIN [dbo].[MUD_REGIONS] MR ON MF.FIPS = MR.FIPS WHERE MF.STATUS_ID != 'R' AND MF.ZIP NOT IN (SELECT ZIP FROM [dbo].[MUD_STAGING])
